testsuite.name: Firefox 67.0 (Windows 7)

property.name: browser.fullName
property.value: Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.1; Win64; x64; rv:67.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/67.0

testcase.name: HeaderComponent should handle navigate home event
AppGuard should return TRUE for canDeativate if the current Component does not have a canDeactivate
AppGuard should return the value of a Components canDeactivate function as canDeactivate
AppGuard should not canActivate when not logged in and navigate to /login
AppGuard should canActivate when logged in
AnosHttpClient should enrich the header of a GET with Authorization when logged in
AnosHttpClient should enrich the header of a PUT with Authorization when logged in
AnosHttpClient should pass down DELETE and call extractToken
AnosHttpClient should enrich the header of a POST with Authorization when logged in
AnosHttpClient should pass down POST and call extractToken
AnosHttpClient should pass down GET and call extractToken
AnosHttpClient should pass down PUT and call extractToken
AnosHttpClient should refresh token when updateTokenTrigger is fired
AnosHttpClient should create a Header without Authorization when no not logged in
AnosHttpClient should create a Header with Authorization when none given when logged in
AnosHttpClient should enrich the header of a DELETE with Authorization when logged in
AnosHttpClient should not enrich a Header with Authorization when no not logged in
ButtonComponent should put the icon after the TEXT if iconName is given and buttonPosition is "right"
ButtonComponent should place an Icon in front of the TEXT if iconName is given
ButtonComponent should add the class smallText if smallText is TRUE
ButtonComponent should have buttonId as the buttons ID
ButtonComponent should not contain a link when no HREF is given
ButtonComponent should contain a link when a HREF is given
ButtonComponent should contain a link with target, when href and hrefTarget are given
ButtonComponent setting buttonDisable to TRUE disables the button
LoginService should extract and refresh token from responses with headers in lowercase
LoginService should fire a updateTokenTrigger 5 minutes after last update
LoginService should logout and navigate to login when receiving an error response 401
LoginService should get token from sucessful login
LoginService should extract and refresh token from responses with headers in Upper-Kebab-Case
LoginService should construct correct body for login request
SideNavContainerComponent should close sidebars when user triggers a route change
SideNavContainerComponent should only display one sidebar menu
SideNavContainerComponent should toggle main navigation (left) sidebar
SideNavContainerComponent should toggle profile navigation (top) sidebar
